categories: Category:Imperial Navy admirals of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: The cousin of Voss Parck was an officer in the Imperial Navy from its foundation.
The man attended the Corulag Academy with his cousin, Voss Parck, with whom he was rivals.

He later graduated and served as the captain of Darth Vader's ship on the mission to Honoghr in which the Dark Lord of the Sith recruited the Noghri, almost immediately after the formation of the Galactic Empire. For his part in that mission, Parck's cousin was promoted to the rank of vice admiral.
Soon afterwards, Voss Parck hoped to gain a similar promotion by recruiting Mitth'raw'nuruodo into the Empire's service.
